attachments.text: For rent: $850. Located near Brady Street's shopping, boutiques, restaurants, & nightlife entertainment this spacious exposed wood beams & Cream City Brick Studio Condo has an open living area with an abundance of natural light & radiantly heated polished concrete floors throughout. Large Full Bathroom with Jetted Tub & heated towel rack. Separate Kitchen with ALL Appliances including a Dishwasher, Disposal, Refrigerator, Stove, & brand new Microwave. Wall Air Conditioner, In-unit Humidifier, Ceiling Fan, California Closet, custom Blinds, Storage Locker, & HEAT all included in rent. The Building features a Laundry Room, Rec/Game Room, Secured Lobby, Intercom System, & individual Floor Level Security Cameras. Street parking available. Pets are negotiable and strictly subject to owner approval.
